                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-601-18370130 t18370130-601-punishment-98"></join>Transported for Seven years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BUGG</hi>.—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18370130-601-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
